Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: uwosh.ATImageEditor
Version: 0.2rc1.1
Summary: A product that adds an editor tab to ATImage so you can crop and resize an image
Home-page: http://plone.org/products/atimageeditor
Author: Nathan Van Gheem
Author-email: vangheem@gmail.com
License: GPL
Description: Introduction
        ============
        Once installed this product adds a "Visual Transform" tab for the image content type.
        With this you can rotate, flip, resize and crop all ajax enabled.
        Changelog
        =========
        
        0.2rc1.1
        ----------------
        *fixed IE critical bug for cropping image that is zoomed
        
        0.2rc1
        ----------------
        *fixed IE bugs and tightened support for advanced features
        
        0.2b3
        ----------------
        *added versioning support
        
        0.2b1
        ----------------
        *mobile actions window
        *undo/redo
        *blur, compression, brightness, contrast
        *shows image size and pixel count
        *warning if user has unsaved changes
        
        0.1rc2
        ----------------
        
        *Added scaling capabilities
        *fixed a few bugs
        
        0.1rc1 - Initial Release
        ----------------
        
        * Initial release
        
        
